C# IEnumerable Extension Methods

StreamChunks - like .Chunk but returns IEnumerable<IEnumerable<T>> with no buffering

AllCombinationsOf - returns all combinations of a set of n items from a source IEnumerable<T>.

AllPermutationsOf - returns all permutations of a set of n items from a source IEnumerable<T>.

RandomSelection - returns a random selection of n items from a source IEnumerable<T>.